</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I've been tooling around with Trip's Magelo Wish List, looking at items I can get for her at 60+ without a raid force. Now, I know the importance of getting AC to 1k, which won't be a problem with Paladin buffs stacked atop Shaman buffs, so I've been looking at HPs-vs-Mana. I want to keep a good balance, so I do want some FT as well. (I'm assuming Ornate Chain Bracers, Solstice Earring and Broken Skull Symbol of Leadership are more than enough, which would bring me to FT9 with MC3, FT12 if I tried for Boots of Flowing Slime.)<br />
<br />
How much Mana is enough? And how many HPs? At what point should I stop focusing on one and focus more on the other?</p>
	
	
	
	
	
