	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>0 Mana can be enough. Enough hp/ac that you dont visit your bind point is also enough, and those numbers will vary widely depending on how well you play and what you fight. Getting a solstice earring incidentally adds ft, but when I got mine it was for some added hp. Cannibalize > FT by a pretty large margin, and I never missed not having any.</p>
	
	
	
