	<p>A goal I shot for was 1K+ AC unbuffed, 2100+ HP's unbuffed and 3K+ mana unbuffed. This was accomplished also without raid forces as I am in a casual, small guild. I feel it's a comfortable level that allows me to rarely go OOM and affords me a slight sense of security that I won't get decimated so long as I'm careful.</p>
	
	
	
