	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I only agree to a point on this topic.  Once u have about 3500+ unbuffed hps u can use Can5 in most situations and avoid low hp agro, after that FT starts to become more important.  Additionally in PoP Uber mob fights many of them are short and their is simply no time to use cannablize, u will simply be chain casting because the mobs die fast.  In these scenarios FT and Manapool become alot more important.  <br />
<br />
Never forgot that these things all stack, there is no reason to sell ureself short, by upgrading ure gear thats strong in one aspect and weak in another.  If u stick with gear thats a good mix of everything be it focuus effects, hps, mana, ft, regen whatever in the end ull find the most use out of it.</p>
	
	
	
